beer.beer_description:
Hello to Grandad Brown! The can says:
We still can't get over the love for our humble English Brown Ale. The first beer we brewed and still delivering classic flavours of caramel, coffee, chocolate and nuts, balanced by Australian hops. A hint of sweetness, a touch of caramel rye, low bitterness and a glowing reddish-brown pour make Grandad Brown love the biggest glass you've got.
